title: The Last Trophy (1960) Full Length Bonanza Western

sources.title: The Last Trophy (1960) Full Length Bonanza Western
sources.description:
A British couple visits the Cartwrights - and the woman (Hazel Court) thinks her own husband is a coward. Everything changes when the couple is kidnapped for ransom along with Adam Cartwright. Edward Ashley and Bert Freed guest star.
 
Director: Lewis Allen
Writer: Bill S. Ballinger
Stars: Dan Blocker, Michael Landon, Lorne Greene
Genres: Classics, Cult, TV, Western
